kdeconnect-kde (Integrate Android with the Plasma Desktop)

KDE Connect is a module to connect KDE with your smartphone.
Prominent features are: clipboard share, notifications sync,
multimedia remote control over secured network connections.
Please note you will need to install KDE Connect on Android
for this app to work:
 https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.kde.kdeconnect_tp

See also:
 https://albertvaka.wordpress.com/2013/08/05/introducing-kde-connect/
